snippet.title: NAKWON: LAST PARADISE Official Teaser
snippet.description:
This is "NAKWON: LAST PARADISE" Governing Committee.
We unveil the inside of the City filled with Zombies and the performance of Survivors who, despite the danger, try their best to secure Resources and contribute to NAKWON.

The information and continuous updated of NAKWON can be found below:
Steam: https://nexon.link/d1q
Official Discord: https://discord.gg/nakwon
Official X(Twitter): https://x.com/nakwonGame
Web: https://mintrocketgames.com/en/nakwon

Join NAKWON 1st Giveaway event and get total $100 steam gift cards!: https://gleam.io/f4vMw/nakwon-1st-giveaway
